= Amazon Tags

== Requirements

* "amazon-ecs" gem package (gem install amazon-ecs)

== Install

1. Change directory to $RADIANT_ROOT/vendor/extension
   $RADIANT_ROOT is the directory of your project directory of radiant.

2. Get extensions.

   git clone git://github.com/vividtone/radiant-amazon-tags.git

3. Set your AWS(Amazon Web Services) information at the tail of 
   $RADIANT_ROOT/config/environment.rb

   [example]
   Radiant::Config["amazon_tags.aws_access_key_id"] = 'your access key id'
   Radiant::Config["amazon_tags.aws_secret_key"] = 'your secret key'
   Radiant::Config["amazon_tags.associate_tag"] = 'your associate tag'
   Radiant::Config["amazon_tags.country"] = 'jp' # country
